in the state courthouse,

29:46.767 --> 29:48.166
not far from
the capital building

29:48.233 --> 29:50.066
where the governor has
ruled with an iron fist

29:50.133 --> 29:51.433
for the past year.

29:51.500 --> 29:53.367
